## t_range3 has partition management, logical partition equal, pwj
EXPLAIN select * from t_range1 t1 intersect select * from t_range3 t2;
Query Plan
==================================================================
|ID|OPERATOR                      |NAME    |EST.ROWS|EST.TIME(us)|
------------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |PX COORDINATOR                |        |12      |35          |
|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR          |:EX10000|12      |29          |
